Power Desktop 98 -32 bit desktop addons & tools

Desktop Themes
Over 250 All New Themes from 1998. Anime, Nature, SouthPark, StarWars, SailorMoon, Pamela Anderson, Titanic, & X Files are just a few examples of the hundreds of high quality themes that are included on this CD ROM. Many Desktop Utilities are also provided to help ease installation of each theme, allowing you to preview the wallpaper, icons, cursors, sounds, colors & fonts without the use of Microsoft Plus! You can even create your own custom made themes.

Screen Savers
Over 100 Awesome NEW ScreenSavers for your viewing pleasure ! The Dancing Baby, Degeneration X, Direct X, Open GL, Simpsons, 3D FX, SouthPark & Fractal Clouds are just some of the eye pleasing screensavers can be easily previewed or installed with the click of the mouse button. There are also several different programs that will allow you to design your own spectacular screensavers.

Fonts & Icons
No Desktop CD ROM would be complete without hundreds of new True Type Fonts for Windows 95/98/NT. There are also font viewers and installers provided on the CD which allow you to view all fonts before installing. You can also use our all new browser, which helps in finding the right font for the job, quickly and easily. Perfect for all Graphics Artists and Web Designers. As an extra bonus there are also hundreds of Desktop Icons which can be used for any programs.
